item.title: CVE-2022-35226|2024-08-03T09:29:17.458Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20data%20services%20management%20console
item.description: SAP Data Services Management allows an attacker to copy the data from a request and echoed into the application's immediate response, it will lead to a Cross-Site Scripting vulnerability. The attacker would have to log in to the management console to perform such as an attack, only few of the pages are vulnerable in the DS management console.
